data.description: Nestled alongside the lush green space of Holt Middle School, this home's prime location allows for walkable access to nearby schools and scenic trails. With 3 beds, 2 baths, & a generous 2,323 sqft, this home is perfect for a growing family. As you step inside, you are greeted by the recessed ceilings and hardwood floors. The kitchen is adorned with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample counter & cabinet space. The living room is made extra cozy this time of year by the fireplace. The bedrooms are spacious & carpeted. This home also features a bonus room. The primary suite features a recessed ceiling and a private bath with a whirlpool, dual vanity, a walk-in shower, and a closet. The fenced-in backyard offers a perfect space for entertaining. Schedule a showing today!
